Ing '''Balaghat''' metung yang lakanbalen o ciudad ampong metung a [[w:municipality|municipality]] king [[w:Balaghat district|distritu ning Balaghat]]  king estadu ning [[Madhya Pradesh]], [[India]]. Iti ing pun tanggapang kapanibalan (''administrative headquarters'') ning [[Balaghat District]]. Sadia, "Burha" o "Boora" ing lagiu ning balen, oneng mialilan ya ini king "Burha" or "Boora", a lagiu na mu ning distritu aniang purmeru. Ing buri nang sabian ning Balaghat, "above the ghats or passes" (king babo da reing ghat [pasu o dalan/gasgas king bunduk]).  

